title: Git branching model.png
comments.comment: Branch earlier and branch often, this is Git's view of the world. ﻿; I like this branching model and have been using it for a few years now.; Atlassian SourceTree has git-flow built in. Easier to follow and easier to enforce this good practice.﻿; http://blog.sourcetreeapp.com/2012/08/01/smart-branching-with-sourcetree-and-git-flow/; I have no doubt that SourceTree works well with this branching model, but I think I'll stick with the command line - I've changed development environments many times over the years and each workplace has their own preferred tools - the command line is more likely to be common.
